{"tid":1019927,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝗蟲雙語爆粗　狂罵機巴車長︰你以為媽X在大陸？","createTime":"2019-02-13T09:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T00:39:55.000Z","uid":225464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae4e0ab92e76c0b90805daf6e755305ebe53a7f","tid":1019927,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>內地阿叔雙語爆粗　狂罵機巴車長︰你以為媽X在大陸？</strong><br />\n<br />\n片LINK：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WW2PoF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WW2PoF&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiVIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=f590701a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WW2PoF</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/photo/bkn-20190213133431026-0213_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190213140314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190213%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190213133431026-0213_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190213140314&h=f89ea47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為乜要咁激動呢？<br />\n<br />\n最近巴士乘客與車長的爭吵日益增多，早前有車長甚至被打也不敢還擊。近日網上再度流出影片，只見有大叔不斷以中英文粗口狂罵車長，惹來網民怒斥︰「黐X線」。<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期二（12日）被上傳至Facebook群組「巴士的事討論區」，只見該輛機場巴士停在旺角維景酒店巴士站附近，有大叔怒氣沖沖地站在車長旁邊，以英文斥道︰「你叫我企喺黃線後&hellip;你話我同佢哋一樣X街」！<br />\n<br />\n車長未多作解釋，只是着他走回車廂內，以免影響其他乘客。但大叔仍情緒激動，改以普通話罵謂︰「你以為老子傻X北佬啊？你以為真的媽X到了大陸啊？X你媽」！<br />\n<br />\n不少網民怒斥大叔黐線︰「原來大聲就贏」、「英文咁差仲好意思用英文鬧人」。有人建議車長報警︰「嚴重騷擾車長駕駛，可能會引致交通意外」、「畀我係車長就熄匙落車」。<br />\n<br />\n想知當時情況有幾激烈？即刻睇片！"},{"pid":"807498a3a65a0fbf20b1d6bde92ea4a4cb733b12","tid":1019927,"uid":133528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:52:54.000Z","msg":"狗黎"},{"pid":"acab1814ae803567f646798cafa2a4f54005e591","tid":1019927,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔少巴士佬都係寸寸貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f549c7847642ef5953b2902c8c81fd45b663b3","tid":1019927,"uid":2772,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"acab1814ae803567f646798cafa2a4f54005e591","tid":1019927,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔少巴士佬都係寸寸貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"但係全部支那人都係低賤生物喎"},{"pid":"4b70813436186348cba7b009544e9a2b00a42014","tid":1019927,"uid":25221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ae7d92aabdcbf1502c74b2bb0a202251c102b59","tid":1019927,"uid":133806,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"acab1814ae803567f646798cafa2a4f54005e591","tid":1019927,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔少巴士佬都係寸寸貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T10:36:45.000Z","msg":"覺得巴士佬串，態度惡劣嘅，大可以同巴士公司投訴，如果個巴士佬本身係衰格嘅話，佢都會有後果，但唔代表可以當住人面咁樣侮辱人嘅。<br />\n<br />\n掉返轉講，而家越嚟越多乘客恃住自己係客，自己永遠都啱晒，巴士佬冇後台就恰鳩人，得閒又冚人幾巴，質人幾槌，再唔係就擋住人架車，或者串鳩人低賤啦，呢啲你唔講？"},{"pid":"ee91870d8afd9768a0694a75e92fe26cb4aa2422","tid":1019927,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"大陸狗"},{"pid":"3d0023dfba7349ff051ee3eaca51462c884556a5","tid":1019927,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T22:44:05.000Z","msg":"鄰近地區人型生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20e3d64d76e9f05b72f86e35979670d810a7001","tid":1019927,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:05:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母大陸噪音狗，講到最尾咪又係用反蝗語，架巴士有中英對照小學雞都識照對"},{"pid":"a420c3090d00c9c20a264a2c101e682817d3f0c8","tid":1019927,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e20e3d64d76e9f05b72f86e35979670d810a7001","tid":1019927,"uid":185213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:05:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母大陸噪音狗，講到最尾咪又係用反蝗語，架巴士有中英對照小學雞都識照對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:06:02.000Z","msg":"照讀"},{"pid":"6f63d65a17f2471fc21d29d3474c10bae8146f95","tid":1019927,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T00:39:55.000Z","msg":"話自己唔同北佬<br />\n但個格係完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}